Module com.example.gui_programming
Package banking_gui

Class Constants

java.lang.Object
banking_gui.Constants
public class Constants extends Object
Provides constant values for managing dates and time. This class contains constants used throughout the project to avoid magic numbers and improve readability.
Author:
Altay Ozkan, Jeffery Sypytkowski
